---
<AdventureLayout title="?" description="A small, mysterious room.">
  <p class="room-title">A Small, Mysterious Room</p>

  <div class="desc">{`You step through the small door. The room beyond is empty
except for a single brass lantern on a low table and a slim
volume titled "TALES: Text Adventure Learning Environment Suite."
Pinned to the lantern is a sticky note:

  "Curious whether you're better than an LLM at a text
   adventure? Visit the TALES project page and click on the
   'Environments' tab — you can try Zork I yourself."

The note is signed C.Z.C.`}</div>

  <p style="font-family: var(--mono); margin-top: 1.4em;">
    &gt; <a href="https://microsoft.github.io/tale-suite/">take lantern</a>
    &nbsp;<span style="color: var(--ink-dim);">(opens the TALES project page)</span>
  </p>

  <RoomNav />
</AdventureLayout>
